<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>自動掃碼簽到系統</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-md-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="mb-4">自動掃碼簽到系統</h1>
        <div class="card shadow">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title mb-4">歡迎使用自動掃碼簽到系統</h2>
            <p class="card-text">這是一個簡單易用的掃碼簽到系統，可用於會議、課程、活動等場景。</p>
            
            <div class="row mt-5">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card mb-3">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">參與者</h3>
                    <p>掃描活動QR碼即可快速簽到</p>
                    <p><i class="bi bi-qr-code"></i></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card mb-3">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">管理員</h3>
                    <p>創建活動並管理簽到記錄</p>
                    <a href="/admin" class="btn btn-primary">進入管理頁面</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>